videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald throws to Stephen Guidry, who fights through a defender and stretches the ball over the goal line for a Mississippi State touchdown.
videos.headline: Guidry fights for end zone on Mississippi State TD

videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald finds a wide open Deddrick Thomas, who makes a cut and finds the end zone for a 36-yard Mississippi State touchdown.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald throws 36-yard TD

videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald throws a dime to Kylin Hill at the goal line for a 23-yard touchdown to extend Mississippi State's lead over Louisiana Tech.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald throws 3rd TD pass in 1st quarter

videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald rifles a pass to Jesse Jackson from 10 yards out for his 4th touchdown pass of the 1st half vs. Louisiana Tech.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald tacks on 4th TD pass in 1st half

videos.description: Aeris Williams goes untouched up the middle for a 29-yard touchdown run to extend Mississippi State's lead over Louisiana Tech.
videos.headline: Mississippi State RB takes it 29 yards to the house
